      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a benchmark example of the S54-powered era, featuring a high-revving 3.2L straight-six with impeccable VANOS timing and crisp individual throttle body response. The chassis is structurally pristine, having undergone proactive subframe reinforcement to ensure long-term torsional rigidity. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock that remains tight and responsive. Every suspension component is factory-spec, maintaining the intended kinematic balance and damping characteristics. With original paint and a showroom-quality interior, this vehicle offers a mechanically pure driving experience for the discerning collector.",
