      "description": "Offering a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen rain or snow. The exterior finish is flawless, featuring deep, mirror-like paint with a professional-grade ceramic coating and zero rock chips or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather still retains its original scent, and there is absolutely no bolster wear or fading on the touchpoints. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has a comprehensive, document-backed service history with all scheduled maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts. The engine bay is concours-clean, showing no signs of leaks or age. The undercarriage is equally pristine. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a turn-key example of a modern classic. I welcome pre-purchase inspections at any local specialist to verify this vehicle's peerless condition.",
